01:36:23.364 --> 01:36:29.928
- You're all right. You're safe.
- Thank you.

01:36:30.137 --> 01:36:33.129
I've go back and get those clothes
before I forget where they are.

01:36:33.340 --> 01:36:35.035
Here, eat something.

01:38:33.427 --> 01:38:38.592
I'm just trying to say...

01:38:44.271 --> 01:38:47.240
people screaming out loud...

01:38:47.441 --> 01:38:49.102
that God is hiding...

01:38:49.310 --> 01:38:52.871
that we failed and
that God is punishing us.

01:38:54.014 --> 01:38:58.678
This is not what is happening. God,
it's not. This is not the God's way.

01:39:01.855 --> 01:39:06.121
What is happening to us reminds
me of what happened to St. Paul.

01:39:06.393 --> 01:39:10.124
Paul used to kill Christians,
used to persecute them...

01:39:10.331 --> 01:39:13.459
but the Lord came to
him and converted him.

01:39:13.667 --> 01:39:16.659
And not only converted him,
but blinded him.

01:39:17.304 --> 01:39:20.034
This is what's happening to us.

01:39:34.121 --> 01:39:35.588
- Here!
- Here!

01:39:35.789 --> 01:39:38.053
- Here I am!
- Here!

01:39:39.293 --> 01:39:42.091
Here.
Here, I have a jacket.

01:39:42.296 --> 01:39:45.595
- I have a jacket.
- Thank you.

01:41:16.457 --> 01:41:17.617
That's terrible.

01:41:18.225 --> 01:41:21.524
- Who would do that?
- Someone who went blind.

01:41:21.729 --> 01:41:24.596
And then he went crazy.
Since he couldn't see...

01:41:24.798 --> 01:41:26.663
he didn't want his statue to see.

01:41:26.867 --> 01:41:28.994
- I don't think so, little man.
- I don't know if it'd be possible...

01:41:29.203 --> 01:41:31.899
for a blind man to paint
the painting like that.

01:41:32.106 --> 01:41:34.040
- Yes, they could.
- Or likely a priest...

01:41:34.241 --> 01:41:38.371
who saw what happened,
and had a crisis of faith.

01:41:39.146 --> 01:41:42.946
No, but seriously, all those people
made me think of how lucky we are...

01:41:43.150 --> 01:41:45.209
that we have a leader with vision.

01:41:45.686 --> 01:41:49.122
So, I think it's up to you to
decide what we should do next.

01:41:49.923 --> 01:41:51.356
Well...

01:41:51.558 --> 01:41:55.255
I think we should stay here tonight,
try to get some sleep.

01:41:55.462 --> 01:42:00.866
And then, tomorrow, I was thinking
that we could go to our house.

01:42:01.068 --> 01:42:04.663
<i>It's pretty near here,
and it's big...</i>

01:42:04.872 --> 01:42:07.568
<i>so it can accommodate everybody.</i>

01:42:12.045 --> 01:42:13.945
Where are you, dog?
Still there?

01:42:14.148 --> 01:42:17.777
No. Don't follow that dog.
He'll lead you to a fire hydrant.

01:42:17.985 --> 01:42:21.978
Too proud to be a seeing eye dog.

01:42:43.010 --> 01:42:45.410
<i>Twenty seven.
Five four.</i>

01:42:45.612 --> 01:42:48.376
<i>Black hair.
Brown eyes.</i>

01:42:48.849 --> 01:42:50.441
<i>I don't wanna know
what you look like.</i>

01:42:50.651 --> 01:42:52.846
<i>But how can we know each other?</i>

01:42:53.053 --> 01:42:56.284
<i>I know that part inside
of you with no name.</i>

01:42:56.757 --> 01:42:59.624
<i>And that's who we are, right?</i>

01:43:06.433 --> 01:43:08.833
<i>When you went to look for food,
we talked to this man...</i>

01:43:09.036 --> 01:43:11.129
<i>that was part of a group
that moved around together...</i>

01:43:11.338 --> 01:43:13.033
<i>trying to find food and shelter.</i>

01:43:13.240 --> 01:43:15.504
<i>Each night they slept
in a different place.</i>

01:43:15.709 --> 01:43:18.769
<i>I asked him why he didn't
sleep in his own home.</i>

01:43:19.213 --> 01:43:21.443
<i>And he said he didn't know
where it was anymore.</i>

01:43:21.648 --> 01:43:23.275
<i>- Yeah, he lost it.
- They're welcome to it...</i>

01:43:23.484 --> 01:43:26.248
<i>if they can find their
way to my little room.</i>

01:43:27.554 --> 01:43:30.352
I think it's okay. Here we are.

01:43:30.557 --> 01:43:33.526
Here we are. Looks fine.
Come in. Come in.

01:43:33.727 --> 01:43:35.888
I can't believe it.

01:43:38.298 --> 01:43:40.596
It's exciting.

01:43:42.302 --> 01:43:45.032
Okay. Careful. Just because
the door was locked...

01:43:45.239 --> 01:43:47.002
doesn't mean that no one's here.

01:43:47.207 --> 01:43:49.141
Hello! Hello!

01:43:49.343 --> 01:43:51.402
Hello! Is anyone here?

01:43:51.612 --> 01:43:53.409
Maybe we should take
our shoes off. Right?

01:43:53.614 --> 01:43:55.582
That's a good idea.
You can leave them by the door.

01:43:55.849 --> 01:43:58.477
We don't wanna mess the place up.
We just arrived.

01:43:58.685 --> 01:44:01.381
If you wanna take off
your clothes too...

01:44:01.588 --> 01:44:03.385
we have plenty of
clean ones upstairs.

01:44:03.590 --> 01:44:05.285
- Thank you.
- Are you talking to me?

01:44:05.492 --> 01:44:09.826
No, to everyone. Our clothes
are just as dirty as our shoes.

01:44:10.964 --> 01:44:13.262
- Here? All together?
- Come on!

01:44:13.467 --> 01:44:15.526
She's the only one who can see!

01:44:15.736 --> 01:44:18.364
If it makes you feel better,
it's getting pretty dark.

01:44:18.572 --> 01:44:20.597
All right.
If you insist.

01:44:20.807 --> 01:44:23.367
I'm sure you've seen worse
sights than this old body.

01:44:24.845 --> 01:44:28.008
I want you to feel at home here
because this is your home now too.

01:44:29.082 --> 01:44:33.485
Thank you both. We're all flattered
that you would offer your home.

01:44:33.687 --> 01:44:34.517
It's our pleasure.

01:44:34.721 --> 01:44:36.621
Kick us out when you had enough.

01:44:37.090 --> 01:44:39.081
Or when I become
too much of a burden.

01:44:39.293 --> 01:44:42.490
Just tell me, and I'll just
wander off like an elephant.

01:44:42.696 --> 01:44:45.494
- You're not an elephant.
- I'm not a man, either.

01:44:45.699 --> 01:44:46.961
- You're plenty of a man, babe.
- I...

01:44:50.971 --> 01:44:52.734
I don't know.

01:44:55.709 --> 01:44:59.509
I haven't seen myself in so long.
I must look ridiculous.

01:44:59.713 --> 01:45:05.049
No, no. Dirty and skinny.
But not ridiculous. Not at all.

01:45:05.852 --> 01:45:08.514
- And what about me?
- You're beautiful.

01:45:08.722 --> 01:45:10.280
Yeah. Not like you.

01:45:10.991 --> 01:45:13.926
- You've never seen me.
- But in my dreams you're beautiful.

01:45:14.127 --> 01:45:17.358
How come you never appeared in my
dreams but I know you're beautiful?

01:45:17.564 --> 01:45:21.091
Well, that's why blindness
is a gift to the ugly.

01:45:21.401 --> 01:45:23.096
- Come on, you're not serious.
- No...

01:45:23.303 --> 01:45:26.136
but I suppose I was
more beautiful before!

01:45:26.340 --> 01:45:28.865
We were all more beautiful before.

01:45:29.376 --> 01:45:31.241
Is anyone cold?

01:45:32.079 --> 01:45:36.038
- It feels so good!
- I'm having a great time!

01:45:52.899 --> 01:45:53.991
Hello?

01:45:54.201 --> 01:45:56.294
It's me.

01:46:04.277 --> 01:46:08.236
- I brought you some hot water.
- Oh, thank you.

01:46:08.448 --> 01:46:11.815
- I'm gonna pour it down, okay?
- Okay.

01:46:15.055 --> 01:46:17.489
- Feels good?
- Feels good.

01:46:33.707 --> 01:46:36.733
<i>I hope we can find
the boy's parents.</i>

01:46:38.412 --> 01:46:40.141
<i>What do you hope for?</i>

01:46:40.347 --> 01:46:44.010
<i>Nothing is more ridiculous than
the desires of an old man.</i>

01:46:44.217 --> 01:46:46.378
<i>Tell me. Iwanna know.</i>

01:46:47.721 --> 01:46:49.848
<i>You wouldn't understand.</i>

01:46:50.057 --> 01:46:52.389
- Why that tone of voice?
- What tone?

01:46:52.626 --> 01:46:54.560
That one.

01:46:57.264 --> 01:47:01.792
What I hope is that we
can go on living together.

01:47:02.235 --> 01:47:05.329
- As we are. Like this.
- Blind?

01:47:06.473 --> 01:47:10.034
For me nothing has been better.

01:47:12.879 --> 01:47:17.316
- I'd want us to live together.
- Together with me, or with everyone?

01:47:18.518 --> 01:47:20.645
Don't make me say.

01:47:21.955 --> 01:47:24.014
I want to know.

01:47:24.791 --> 01:47:27.089
Are we alone?

01:47:29.730 --> 01:47:32.426
Is anyone listening?

01:47:35.368 --> 01:47:37.029
Good.

01:47:37.504 --> 01:47:38.994
Good.

01:47:39.206 --> 01:47:41.731
I wanna live with you.

01:47:53.587 --> 01:47:56.351
I remember that New Year's.

01:47:57.758 --> 01:48:01.558
It was cold, but I didn't mind.

01:48:11.071 --> 01:48:15.007
All right. At this end of the table
we have pees and carrots.

01:48:15.208 --> 01:48:20.077
At the center we've olives in a bowl
and some crackers on a small plate.

01:48:20.280 --> 01:48:23.272
And, at the far end of the table,
we have anchovies.

01:48:23.917 --> 01:48:25.407
Anchovies!

01:48:25.619 --> 01:48:28.144
Don't we have a special bottle of
something sparkling for our guests?

01:48:28.355 --> 01:48:31.654
There's nothing like water.
Clean water.

01:48:32.993 --> 01:48:35.757
I'd like to propose a toast.
To our family.

01:48:36.730 --> 01:48:38.994
- To our human family.
- And the dog!

01:48:40.367 --> 01:48:43.234
- And the dog!
- And the dog! And the dog!

01:48:43.436 --> 01:48:46.200
- Salute!
- Salute!

01:48:46.473 --> 01:48:49.135
Much better than any champagne.

01:49:03.924 --> 01:49:06.449
I see you.

01:49:10.597 --> 01:49:15.625
When I touch you like this,
I see your face.

01:49:15.836 --> 01:49:17.895
So beautiful.

01:49:18.772 --> 01:49:21.707
It's all I need to remember.

01:49:27.681 --> 01:49:31.674
- Tell me, is this working?
- Let's see. You take another one.

01:49:31.885 --> 01:49:34.319
Take another of me in the face.

01:49:34.521 --> 01:49:36.352
Blind inspiration.

01:49:36.656 --> 01:49:39.921
There's coffee,
if anybody wants some.

01:49:40.126 --> 01:49:43.527
- I'll have some, please.
- I want some too.

01:49:45.165 --> 01:49:46.427
I need to wake up.

01:49:46.633 --> 01:49:48.624
Honey? Honey?

01:49:49.169 --> 01:49:54.004
I think we should get together
and talk about what we need to do.

01:49:54.374 --> 01:49:57.741
There's not much food left,
and I'm worried about security.

01:49:59.045 --> 01:50:01.809
- Okay.
- I can pour it for you.

01:50:10.457 --> 01:50:12.584
It's hot.

01:50:17.364 --> 01:50:19.161
It's you.

01:50:20.000 --> 01:50:24.061
It's you! Oh, my God!
It's everyone at here.

01:50:24.671 --> 01:50:25.831
Hi.

01:50:26.106 --> 01:50:28.404
- What?
- I can see you!

01:50:29.075 --> 01:50:32.101
- What are you saying?
- I can see you!

01:50:33.146 --> 01:50:34.841
- What?
- Yes.

01:50:35.048 --> 01:50:37.516
- What are you talking about?
- Everything is beautiful!

01:50:38.785 --> 01:50:39.979
I can...

01:50:40.186 --> 01:50:41.210
- What?
- Oh, my God!

01:50:41.421 --> 01:50:43.150
- What do you mean, you can see?
- Hey, you! I can see you.

01:50:43.356 --> 01:50:45.324
I got back my sight!

01:50:46.526 --> 01:50:49.120
- What is it?
- Come here.

01:50:49.529 --> 01:50:50.655
- I can see!
- How?

01:50:50.864 --> 01:50:53.128
- I can see!
- You're lying.

01:50:53.333 --> 01:50:57.565
- What?
- Really?

01:50:57.771 --> 01:51:00.865
- You have your sight?
- Yeah!

01:51:01.074 --> 01:51:02.541
You're kidding!

01:51:02.742 --> 01:51:04.403
- You're eyes!
- Nice to meet you.

01:51:04.611 --> 01:51:07.739
- Oh, my God!
- He can see!

01:51:07.948 --> 01:51:11.281
- I can't believe it!
- He sees! He sees!

01:51:11.484 --> 01:51:13.714
- I thought he was kidding!
- No.

01:51:13.920 --> 01:51:17.651
- Hey, you guys!
- What this mean?

01:51:17.857 --> 01:51:19.051
I can see everybody's face!

01:51:19.259 --> 01:51:22.558
- Oh, my gosh!
- I know. I can't believe it!

01:51:22.762 --> 01:51:27.790
I can see you. I love you guys!
You guys are so beautiful!

01:51:28.802 --> 01:51:30.030
<i>At that moment...</i>

01:51:30.236 --> 01:51:33.171
<i>the same unspoken thought
occurred to everyone:</i>

01:51:34.541 --> 01:51:36.805
<i>"He was the first to go blind.
Perhaps...</i>

01:51:37.143 --> 01:51:40.203
<i>we will all regain
our sight in turn. "</i>

01:51:42.515 --> 01:51:46.007
<i>So the celebration was
not entirely selfless.</i>

01:51:51.825 --> 01:51:53.315
<i>The next days,
the next weeks...</i>

01:51:53.526 --> 01:51:56.757
<i>would therefore be
sleepless with anticipation.</i>

01:51:56.963 --> 01:51:59.158
<i>They would see again.</i>

01:51:59.532 --> 01:52:03.798
<i>This time, they would really see.</i>

01:52:05.438 --> 01:52:06.928
<i>But who would be so timid...</i>

01:52:07.140 --> 01:52:10.974
<i>as to cling to this
blanket of blindness?</i>

01:52:11.211 --> 01:52:13.145
<i>Who would be so
foolish as to fear...</i>

01:52:13.346 --> 01:52:16.747
<i>that its intimacies might be lost?</i>

01:52:19.252 --> 01:52:21.220
<i>And what of this woman...</i>

01:52:21.421 --> 01:52:24.185
<i>who is now so strangely silent...</i>

01:52:24.391 --> 01:52:27.792
<i>who has borne such a
terrible weight...</i>

01:52:27.994 --> 01:52:31.862
<i>and is now so suddenly free?</i>

01:52:32.966 --> 01:52:37.335
<i>Already she could imagine the
voices of the city, shouting:</i>

01:52:37.537 --> 01:52:39.903
<i>"I can see!"</i>

01:52:44.344 --> 01:52:46.869
<i>"I'm going blind", she thought.</i>

